Cloud,Lending,Inc,provides,technology,to,assist,small,and,medium,sized,business,to,manage,loan,and,investment,portfolio,for,lending,institutions,The,Cloud,Lending,Inc,platform,allows,creation,of,extensions,for,various,industry,verticals,eg,Auto,P,P,Mortgage,and,Micro,Finance,The,Cloud,Lending,Inc,API,allows,users,to,integrate,with,the,Lending,Core,and,makes,it,possible,to,fully,integrate,the,P,PFlex,with,an,external,website,The,API,lets,users,provide,current,loan,information,to,both,borrowers,and,investors,The,API,can,also,use,the,API,to,create,investor,and,borrower,dashboards,on,the,website